        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>My life in 10 years time, probably on beautifull island in Indonesia with my son. My occupation would be, scuba diving teatcher on a sailboat with friends or family, certainly my son would be dive master too. We would have a house on the beach very closer the sea, with two dogs. That was a beautifull dream, but can be make it happens.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment">A2 grammar errors, B1 vocab and conditional</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
